itinerary.event_name: South Lake Union Outdoor Exploration & Dine-Out

activities.activity_name: Meet and Greet at Lake Union Park
activities.activity_location: Lake Union Park, 860 Terry Ave N, Seattle, WA 98109
activities.description: Gather at the picturesque Lake Union Park to kick start the day's activities.
Beginning from Lake Union Park, head out on a comprehensive walking tour of South Lake Union neighborhood, soaking in the city vibe.
Head to the *Sponsored Location* to indulge in the *Sponsored activity*.

activities.activity_name: Visit to the Museum of History & Industry (MOHAI)
activities.description: Enjoy a visit to the MOHAI to gain insights into the rich history and industry of Seattle.
Conclude the day with a delicious dinner at a popular local restaurant in South Lake Union neighborhood.

activities.activity_name: Leisurely Walk Back to Lake Union Park
activities.activity_location: Lake Union Park, 860 Terry Ave N, Seattle, WA 98109
activities.description: Relax and take in the city's night view as the group leisurely heads back to Lake Union Park.
